# installing


#### step1

~~~ruby
group :development, :test do
  gem 'jasmine'
  gem "jasminerice"
end
~~~

#### step2

    jasmine init

    curl http://cloud.github.com/downloads/velesin/jasmine-jquery/jasmine-jquery-1.2.0.js > spec/javascripts/helpers/jasmine_jquery-1.2.0.js

#### step 3

     vim spec/javascripts/spec.js

     //= require application
     //= require_tree .

     vim spec/javascripts/spec.css

     /*
     *= require application
     */

   

#### step 4

    rails s 
    0.0.0.0/jasmine
